title: Zegra Jungle Empress 1948 Fox Feature Golden Age
description:
Zegra was jungle hero who lived in an African village populated by white women and African males. The Jungle Empress protected her village from threats such as wild animals, invading hostile tribes, and hunters out to hunt human sport. She was assisted by Jono a young boy from her village on one occasion and was also an ally to the French Foreign Legion.
However, Zegra also fought unusual enemies including Flying Death, a group of machine-gun wielding soldiers who rode flying carpets, and the Legion of Mad Mummies.

Real Name
Zegra
First Appearance
Zegra, Jungle Empress #2 (October 1948)
